{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":104,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"好快的刀。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":8,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我果然没有看错你，我从来也没有看见过这么快的刀。","tone":"得意","chapter":15,"line_start":16,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"你还想再看看。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":15,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我不想，我也知道你不会杀我的，用这种刀来杀一个孤苦伶仃的女孩子，小李探花知道了，一定会很生气。","tone":"娇声","chapter":15,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"何况，你本该感激我才是，若不是我昨天叫华子清留下那两包药，你今天也未必能杀了他的。","tone":"娇声","chapter":15,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"可是我也很感激你，你总算已为我杀了一个人了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":15,"line_start":30,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我既已杀了一个人，就还能杀第二个。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我相信。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"所以你最好赶快走。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你又要赶我走。","tone":"无奈","chapter":15,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"是！","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我长得难道比那女道士难看？我难道就不能像她一样的侍候你？","tone":"娇声","chapter":15,"line_start":48,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你要走了？到哪里去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是不是要去找那女道士？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":66,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你若是去找她，我劝你不如躺下去养养神，因为你一定找不到她的。","tone":"淡然","chapter":15,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你若想去找丁灵琳，还不如在这里陪我谈谈心，因为你就算找到了他，也只有觉得更难受。","tone":"淡然","chapter":15,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"也许你现在还能找到一个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"现在你惟一可以找到的人就是韩贞，而且一找就可以找到，你知道为什么？","tone":"淡然","chapter":15,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"因为他已躺在棺材里，连动都不会动了。","tone":"淡然","chapter":15,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你明知道他不是我杀的，瞪着我干什么？你若想替他报仇就该先找出他的仇人来。","tone":"微笑","chapter":15,"line_start":98,"line_end":100},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"可是我劝你不要去，你现在惟一应该做的事，就是躺下去好好睡一觉。","tone":"淡然","chapter":15,"line_start":102,"line_end":102}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_ye_kai","updates":{"one_line":"飞刀传人，叶开此刻心怀愧疚与愤怒。"}},{"id":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","updates":{"one_line":"神秘少女，借刀杀人于无形。"}}]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":105,"line_end":204,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ke_zhan_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"客栈掌柜","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我们发现他的时候，他已经无救了，只好先买口棺材，暂时将他收殓，但我们却连他姓什么都不知道，只希望他还有亲戚朋友来收他的尸。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":112,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ke_zhang_de","text":"谢谢你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":120,"line_end":120},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ke_zhang_de","text":"他怎么死的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_ke_zhan_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"客栈掌柜","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是被一柄剑钉死在床上的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ke_zhang_de","text":"剑呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_ke_zhan_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"客栈掌柜","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"剑还在。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_ke_zhan_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"客栈掌柜","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我们店里的两个伙计，费了很大的力气，才将这柄剑拔出来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":140,"line_end":140},{"speaker":"char_dian_huo_ji","speaker_name":"店伙计","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"跟大爷你一起来住店的那位姑娘，前天晚上也回来过一次，她好像也病了，是被那位击败了南宫远的郭大侠抱回来的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":154,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dian_huo_ji","text":"他们到哪里去了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":158,"line_end":158},{"speaker":"char_dian_huo_ji","speaker_name":"店伙计","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"不知道，他们只出现了一下子。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":160,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_dian_huo_ji","speaker_name":"店伙计","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"那天晚上是我当值，我刚进了院子，就看见屋里有道光芒一闪，就像是闪电一样。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_dian_huo_ji","speaker_name":"店伙计","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"等我赶过去时，大爷你的这位朋友已被钉死在床上。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":166,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_dian_huo_ji","speaker_name":"店伙计","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"然后郭大侠就抱着那位姑娘回来了，郭大侠和南宫远比剑时，我也抽空去看了，所以我认得他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":168,"line_end":168},{"speaker":"char_dian_huo_ji","speaker_name":"店伙计","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"等我去报告了掌柜，再回去看时，郭大侠和那位姑娘又不见了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":172,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ke_zhang_de","text":"这柄剑你能不能让我带走。","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_ke_zhan_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"客栈掌柜","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"当然可以……","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":194,"line_end":194},{"speaker":"char_ke_zhan_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"客栈掌柜","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"大爷你难道不准备收你这位朋友的尸？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":198,"line_end":198},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ke_zhang_de","text":"我会来的，明后天我一定来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":200,"line_end":200}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ke_zhan_zhang_gui","name":"客栈掌柜","alias":"掌柜","identity":"客栈掌柜","faction":"none","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"为韩贞收殓的善良客栈掌柜。","personality":{"traits":["善良","不刻薄","讨好","邀功","实在"],"speech_style":"点头哈腰","temperament":"圆滑"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":112,"line_end":200,"text":"客栈掌柜替叶开讲述韩贞被钉死过程"}]},{"id":"char_dian_huo_ji","name":"店伙计","alias":"伙计","identity":"八方镖局客栈伙计","faction":"none","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"当值的店伙计，曾目睹郭定击败南宫远。","personality":{"traits":["老实","观察细致","机警","胆小","热心"],"speech_style":"平铺直叙","temperament":"谨慎"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":154,"line_end":172,"text":"店伙计补充讲述当晚发生经过"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_song_wen_chang_jian","name":"松纹长剑","type":"weapon","owner":"char_lv_di","one_line":"精钢百炼、剑背带松纹的古雅长剑。","description":"形式古雅的长剑，由精钢百炼而成，非常锋利，剑背上带着松纹。血迹已被黄布包去，是武当弟子专用之剑。","effects":["能以一掷之力贯穿人身钉在床上"],"origin":"武当派","rarity":"上乘佳品","related_characters":["char_lv_di","char_han_zhen"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":136,"line_end":512,"text":"精钢百炼，剑背带松纹，被怀疑为吕迪所有"}]}]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_han_zhen","updates":{"one_line":"已被剑钉死于客栈床上，死因待查。"}}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":205,"line_end":309,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"这里的总镖头就是我。","tone":"沉声","chapter":15,"line_start":234,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你又是什么人？来找谁的？","tone":"沉声","chapter":15,"line_start":242,"line_end":242},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"我就是来找你的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":244,"line_end":244},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"有何见教？","tone":"沉声","chapter":15,"line_start":246,"line_end":246},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"有两件事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":248,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你不妨先说一件。","tone":"沉声","chapter":15,"line_start":250,"line_end":250},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"我要来借五百两银子，三天之内就还给你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":252,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你受了伤。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":254,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你若不想再受一次伤，就最好赶快从你来的那条路滚回去。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":260,"line_end":260},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"我久已听说铁胆镇八方是个横行霸道的人，看来果然没有说错。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":15,"line_start":264,"line_end":264},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"我向你借五百两银子，你可以不借，又何必再要我受一次伤？又何必要我滚回去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":270,"line_end":272},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我就要你滚。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":15,"line_start":274,"line_end":274},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"断！","tone":"厉声","chapter":15,"line_start":286,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"你拗断过几个人的手指了。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":302,"line_end":302},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"你下次要拗断别人的手指时，最好想想此时此刻。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":308,"line_end":308}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_dai_gao_gang","name":"戴高岗","alias":"铁胆镇八方","identity":"八方镖局总镖头","faction":"faction_ba_fang_biao_ju","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"捏铁胆、恃强凌弱的八方镖局总镖头。","personality":{"traits":["横行霸道","傲慢","前倨后恭","善于见风使舵","欺软怕硬"],"speech_style":"粗豪直白","temperament":"暴烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lv_di","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"彼此相识"}],"known_skills":["skill_ying_zhua_li"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":222,"line_end":309,"text":"戴高岗与叶开冲突后反恭"}]}],"skills":[{"id":"skill_ying_zhua_li","name":"鹰爪力","type":"指法","faction":"none","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"以指力抓碎骨肉的外门硬功。","techniques":[{"id":"tech_ying_zhua_li_zhua","name":"鹰爪擒拿","type":"attack","description":"以五指抓取对方衣襟或骨节"}],"progression":[{"level":"初窥门径","chapter":15}],"effects":["抓碎骨节","拗断手指"],"combat_style":"硬抓硬拿","rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":278,"line_end":298,"text":"戴高岗的鹰爪力被叶开反制"}]}],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_ba_fang_biao_ju","name":"八方镖局","type":"帮派","location":"长安","sub_divisions":["总镖头戴高岗","账房"],"one_line":"长安镖局，戴高岗坐镇。","source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":212,"line_end":342,"text":"叶开走入八方镖局"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":310,"line_end":405,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"请留步。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":312,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"你有五百两银子借给我？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":314,"line_end":314},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"朋友尊姓？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"叶。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":318,"line_end":318},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"木叶的叶？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":320,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"叶开？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":324,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"不错，开心的开。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":326,"line_end":326},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"阁下就是叶开？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":15,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"正是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":330,"line_end":330},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"阁下为何不早说？","tone":"苦笑","chapter":15,"line_start":332,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"我并不是来打秋风的，只不过是来借而已，而且只借三天。","tone":"淡然","chapter":15,"line_start":334,"line_end":334},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"五百两已够？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":338,"line_end":338},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"我只不过想买两口棺材。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":340,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_zhang_fang","speaker_name":"账房","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"请收下。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":344,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"阁下刚才是说有两件事的。","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":350,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"我还要打听一个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":354,"line_end":354},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"吕迪，白衣剑客吕迪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":356,"line_end":356},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"据说他已到了长安，你知不知道他在哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":360,"line_end":360},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"就在这里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":362,"line_end":362},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"你就是吕迪？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":368,"line_end":368},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是！","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":370,"line_end":370},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"你认不认得这柄剑？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":374,"line_end":374},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"这是武当的松纹剑。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":376,"line_end":376},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"是不是只有武当弟子才能用这柄剑？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":378,"line_end":378},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":380,"line_end":380},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"你是不是武当弟子？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":382,"line_end":382},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是！","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":384,"line_end":384},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"这是不是你的剑？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":386,"line_end":386},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"不是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":388,"line_end":388},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"你的剑呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":390,"line_end":390},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我近年已不用剑。","tone":"傲然","chapter":15,"line_start":392,"line_end":392},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"用手？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":394,"line_end":394},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"不错，有些人的手，也一样是利器。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":396,"line_end":396},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"可是你若要从窗外杀人，还是得用剑。","tone":"陈述","chapter":15,"line_start":400,"line_end":400}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_lv_di","name":"吕迪","alias":"白衣剑客","identity":"温侯银戟吕凤先之侄，武当弟子","faction":"faction_wu_dang","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"白衣冷漠高傲，惯用手作兵器的武当高手。","personality":{"traits":["高傲","冷漠","自信","光明磊落","惺惺相惜","自负","话多"],"speech_style":"简短傲然","temperament":"冷酷高傲"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lv_feng_xian","type":"亲属","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"侄承叔业"}],"known_skills":["skill_wu_dang_song_wen_jian_fa"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":312,"line_end":405,"text":"吕迪初现，承认自己是武当弟子"}]},{"id":"char_zhang_fang","name":"账房","alias":"机警账房","identity":"八方镖局账房","faction":"faction_ba_fang_biao_ju","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"机警的八方镖局