{"segment":8,"line_start":716,"line_end":820,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你输了。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":762,"line_end":762},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你的体力已无法再支持下去，迟早一定会崩溃，所以你不必出手，我已知道你输了。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":780,"line_end":780}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":9,"line_start":821,"line_end":954,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"手下留情。","tone":"焦急","chapter":15,"line_start":872,"line_end":872},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"你不要我在这里杀他？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":874,"line_end":874},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"你何必一定要杀他？","tone":"无奈","chapter":15,"line_start":876,"line_end":876},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"谁说我要杀他？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":15,"line_start":878,"line_end":878},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"可是你……","tone":"犹豫","chapter":15,"line_start":880,"line_end":880},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"我若真的要杀他，凭你一句话就能拦得住？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":15,"line_start":882,"line_end":882},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"我若真的要杀他，他已死了十次。","tone":"傲然","chapter":15,"line_start":886,"line_end":886},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你可知道我为什么不杀你？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":896,"line_end":896},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"因为你本已受了伤，否则以你轻功之高，纵然不能胜我，我也无法追上你。","tone":"认真","chapter":15,"line_start":900,"line_end":901},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"你根本用不着追，因为我纵然不能胜你，也不会逃的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":15,"line_start":904,"line_end":905},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我相信。","tone":"认真","chapter":15,"line_start":908,"line_end":908},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我相信你绝不是那种人，所以我更不能杀你，因为我还要等你的伤好了以后，再与我一决胜负。","tone":"认真","chapter":15,"line_start":910,"line_end":911},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"你……","tone":"惊讶","chapter":15,"line_start":914,"line_end":914},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"就因为我相信你不会逃，所以知道你一定会来的。","tone":"认真","chapter":15,"line_start":916,"line_end":916},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"到了那一天，我还是败在你手下，你就要杀我了？","tone":"疑问","chapter":15,"line_start":920,"line_end":920},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"到了那一天，你若胜了我，我也情愿死在你手下。","tone":"认真","chapter":15,"line_start":922,"line_end":922},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"世事如棋，变化无常，你又怎知我们一定能等到那一天？","tone":"无奈","chapter":15,"line_start":924,"line_end":924},{"speaker":"char_lv_di","speaker_name":"吕迪","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我知道。","tone":"认真","chapter":15,"line_start":928,"line_end":928},{"speaker":"char_shen_mi_ren","speaker_name":"神秘人","listener":null,"text":"但有件事你却不知道。","tone":"沉声","chapter":15,"line_start":930,"line_end":930},{"speaker":"char_shen_mi_ren","speaker_name":"神秘人","listener":"char_lv_di","text":"今日你若真的想杀他，现在你也已是个死人了，他身上并不只一把刀。","tone":"沉声","chapter":15,"line_start":936,"line_end":937},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我实在想不到你居然会败。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":15,"line_start":944,"line_end":944},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"我也想不到你居然会救我。","tone":"微笑","chapter":15,"line_start":948,"line_end":948},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"并不是我救你的，我也救不了你。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":15,"line_start":950,"line_end":950},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_dai_gao_gang","text":"只要你有这意思，就已足够。","tone":"认真","chapter":15,"line_start":952,"line_end":952},{"speaker":"char_dai_gao_gang","speaker_name":"戴高岗","listener":null,"text":"套马备车。","tone":"严肃","chapter":15,"line_start":954,"line_end":954}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_lv_feng_xian","name":"吕凤先","alias":["温侯银戟"],"identity":"兵器谱上的高手，吕迪的家叔","faction":"武当","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"温侯银戟，兵器谱上成名高手，吕迪的家叔","personality":{"traits":["好胜","不甘人下","执着","刚烈","骄傲"],"speech_style":"不详","temperament":"刚烈好胜"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lv_di","type":"亲属","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"吕迪自幼受其影响练功"}],"known_skills":["skill_wen_hou_yin_ji"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":584,"line_end":584,"text":"他说的就是'温侯银戟'吕凤先。"},{"chapter":15,"line_start":592,"line_end":592,"text":"吕凤先是成名后才开始练的，只练成了三根手指。"},{"chapter":15,"line_start":596,"line_end":596,"text":"兵器谱上排名，温侯银戟在天机神棒、龙凤双环、小李飞刀和嵩阳铁剑之下。"},{"chapter":15,"line_start":604,"line_end":604,"text":"因为吕凤先败了，败在一个女人手下。"}]},{"id":"char_shen_mi_ren","name":"神秘人","alias":[],"identity":"墙外暗中观察的高手，知晓叶开底细","faction":"unknown","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"暗中观察叶开与吕迪决战的神秘高手，出言警告吕迪","personality":{"traits":["沉稳","深不可测","警觉","冷静","洞察力强"],"speech_style":"沉声低语","temperament":"深沉内敛"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[15],"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":930,"line_end":937,"text":"突听墙外一人叹息着道：'但有件事你却不知道。'……'今日你若真的想杀他，现在你也已是个死人了，他身上并不只一把刀。'"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_lv_di","updates":{"rank":"出神入化","source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":576,"line_end":578,"text":"你看清了，这不是手，这是杀人的利器。"},{"chapter":15,"line_start":824,"line_end":824,"text":"吕迪的手，忽然已到了他的胸膛。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_lv_feng_xian","type":"亲属","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"家叔，自幼受其影响练功"},{"action":"update","target":"char_ye_kai","type":"对手","intensity":85,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"惺惺相惜，约定伤愈后再决胜负"}]},{"id":"char_ye_kai","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":836,"line_end":837,"text":"叶开的轻功，竟已达到了'不可能'的境界。"},{"chapter":15,"line_start":900,"line_end":901,"text":"因为你本已受了伤，否则以你轻功之高，纵然不能胜我，我也无法追上你。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_lv_di","type":"对手","intensity":85,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"惺惺相惜，约定伤愈后再决胜负"},{"action":"add","target":"char_dai_gao_gang","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"戴高岗仗义相助，叶开心存感激"}]},{"id":"char_dai_gao_gang","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":15,"line_start":872,"line_end":872,"text":"手下留情。"},{"chapter":15,"line_start":944,"line_end":954,"text":"戴高岗扶起叶开，吩咐套马备车。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_ye_kai","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"戴高岗仗义相助"},{"action":"add","target":"char_lv_di","type":"对手","intensity":30,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"试图劝阻吕迪，但无力阻止"}]}]}
